        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="fCP3ZVzkIydIxqKMDIIO-19" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; {&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;flow_id&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: &quot;alt-001&quot;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;condition&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: &quot;PDF does not have fillable form fields&quot;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;description&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: &quot;Manually determine field locations and add text annotations to the PDF&quot;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;steps&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: [ ...... ],&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;source_text&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: &quot;If the PDF doesn&#39;t have fillable form fields, you&#39;ll need to visually determine where the data should be added and create text annotations. Follow the below steps *exactly*. You MUST perform all of these steps to ensure that the the form is accurately completed. Details for each step are below.&quot;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &quot;&lt;b&gt;provenance&lt;/b&gt;&quot;: &quot;EXPLICIT&quot;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; }&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
